QPR 's Matt Phillips has been in sensational form since the turn of the year and sits second - behind only Barcelona 's Lionel Messi - in the list of top assist makers in Europe 's big five leagues in 2015 .
Phillips set up another two goals for Chris Ramsey 's side in their 3-3 draw with Aston Villa on Tuesday .
Wolfsburg midfielder Kevin de Bruyne has 17 assists in the Bundesliga this year .